Usage: reportDensityMap [-help] [-gridInMicron <micron>] [-gridInRow <nrRow>]
                        [-ignoreBlock {true|false}] [-ignoreFiller {true|false}]
                        [-threshold <density>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-gridInMicron <micron>     # specify the value (in micron) of side of square
                           # grid for density calculations.
                           # (float, default=50, min=0, max=1000)
-gridInRow <nrRow>         # specify the value (in row-height) of side of
                           # square grid for density calculations.
                           # (int, default=10, min=1, max=100)
-ignoreBlock {true|false}  # (bool, default=false)
-ignoreFiller {true|false} # (bool, default=false)
-threshold <density>       # threshold value over which the densities must be
                           # reported. (float, default=0.75, min=0, max=2)